		margin-top: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
	}

	.legal-content p {
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

